        " of 42–42       Nikephoros first attracts the attention of his Byzantine contemporaries and historians for his actions after the Battle of Zygos Pass in 42 Attaleiates records that Nikephoros was able to wield effective command over his mounted troops as he retreated them from being overrun by ": null
